Name: CodeReference
Description: Identifies the value to which the new response domain is attached by a references a specific Code within the CodeDomain.

Name: CategoryReference
Description: Identifies the value to which the new response domain is attached by a references a specific Category within the CategoryDomain.

Name: DomainSpecificValue
Description: Identifies the value to which the new response domain is attached by a reference to a specific value used by the response domain and the specific value.
